-- Amper 2013 Sales To Reach as Much as $691 Million on International Growth
-- B y   M a n u e l   B a i g o r r i
-- 2010-11-29T07:41:14Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-29/amper-2013-sales-to-reach-as-much-as-691-million-on-international-growth.html
Amper SA said it aims to post sales
of as much as 520 million euros in 2013 compared with about 260
million euros this year. Recurring earnings before interest,
taxes, depreciation and amortization may reach 10 million euros
this year, the company said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
